Development of ImageJ and related software relies heavily on [http://git-scm.com/ Git], a first-class [[wikipedia:Distributed version control|distributed]] [[wikipedia:Version control|version control]] system. Git saves "snapshots" of the source code, keeping a history of changes.

See the [[source code]] page for information on where the Git repositories reside.

